"{\"uid\": \"si.com-college-cincinnati-news-look-former-cincinnati-volleyball-wins-silver-at-2024-paris-olympics-01j513v8cgv4\", \"text\": \"CINCINNATI \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00c2\\u00a0Cincinnati alum Jordan Thompson is taking home Olympic silver with the U.S. team after Italy won the gold in straight sets on Sunday. It's another major accomplishment by the Bearcats' contingent as Thompson became the first UC representative in Olympic history to win a pair of medals.  She took home gold with the team at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.  The FIRST two-time Olympic medalist in Cincinnati history. \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u00b8\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#Bearcats|#OlympiansMadeHerepic.twitter.com/Fij8g1e0PZ  It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s@coachphilwhite\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s shirt for us \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b9We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re so proud of you,@jtomm19!#OlympiansMadeHere|#Bearcatspic.twitter.com/C7xwhynqIY  Subscribe to our\\u00c2YouTube channel\\u00c2\\u00a0on all things Bearcats athletics and Bearcat Blitz on\\u00c2Apple Podcasts\\u00c2\\u00a0and\\u00c2Spotify!  Bookmark Bearcats Talk for the latest news, exclusive interviews, film breakdowns\\u00c2\\u00a0and\\u00c2\\u00a0so much\\u00c2\\u00a0more.  You may also like:  Scott Satterfield Updates Dontay Corleone's Status, Bearcats Defensive Line Depth  Tyler Betsey Dives Into Process of Becoming a Cincinnati Bearcat  Recruiting Roundup: Cincinnati Makes Top Schools For Three-Star 2025 Guard Cameron Wallace  Watch: Cincinnati Football Highlights From Opening Days at Camp Higher Ground  Look: Travis Kelce Named Top-10 Player in NFL Top 100  Look: Bearcats Reveal Uniform Combination For Opening Game Against Towson  Report: Cincinnati Football Facing Bowling Green As Final 2025 Non-Conference Opponent  Watch: Brendan Sorsby Laces Deep Ball to Xzavier Henderson  Cincinnati Reds Trade for Bearcats Alum Joey Wiemer in Deadline Deal With Milwaukee Brewers  Look: Sauce Gardner Ranked Outside NFL's 30